Steele Pools is based out of Oakville, ON.  We service Oakville, Burlington, Mississauga, Ancaster, Hamilton and Toronto.  We create custom swimming pools, water features, high end natural stonework, beautiful flagstone patios, outdoor kitchens, and more.   
We pride ourselves on using the highest quality products available and attention to even the smallest details in our workmanship.  
We specialize in Custom swimming pools and natural stonework.
We believe in quality over quantity and building a fantasy backyard oasis to last you and your family years to come.

If you are looking for a company that provides the absolute highest quality service you have come to the right place. We have been in business for over 14 years in which we have provided our top notch services to many happy customers. We specialize in pool renovations, new pools, driveways, patios, porches and more!

With Exterior Pools & Concrete you as the customer are completely taken care of from the moment we arrive, you only deal with one person throughout the process. Not only will you be able to tell us exactly what you want but you will always be able to contact us at any time during the whole process. We treat our customers like family. Leaving you with a smile on your face is extremely important to us because we pride ourselves on quality and excellent treatment to our clients.

We make your dreams a reality and we can guarantee that choosing Exterior Pools and Concrete is the right choice. Please do not hesitate to contact us today in order to book your free consultation with Exterior Pools & Concrete. Send us an email or leave us a message and we can usually get back to you by the end of the day!
